race.comment: BLESSED RAIN (5) was last seen when rocketing around 425m at this track in 23.58 for a 5 length success. In form and looks the one to beat again. CANYA ULTIMATE (8) goes very well at the course and distance with three wins and a placing from five starts. Recorded a one length win (23.60) in a Special conditions H last time at this track. Looks one of the chances. DR. ASHER (1) is a well performed dog and winner of 33 races who was in the minor money last time out at this track (23.65). The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Winning chance. MAV REIKO (7) is among the chances again if he runs up to the latest effort.
